nodes.name: model
nodes.class_name:
SimpleConvNet(
  (conv1): Sequential(
    (0): Conv2d(3, 16, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
    (1): BatchNorm2d(16, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (2): ReLU()
    (3): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
  )
  (conv2): Sequential(
    (0): Conv2d(16, 32, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
    (1): BatchNorm2d(32, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (2): ReLU()
    (3): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
  )
  (conv3): Sequential(
    (0): Conv2d(32, 64, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
    (1): BatchNorm2d(64, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (2): ReLU()
    (3): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
  )
  (conv4): Sequential(
    (0): Conv2d(64, 128, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
    (1): BatchNorm2d(128, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (2): ReLU()
    (3): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
  )
  (skip1): Conv2d(3, 16, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(2, 2))
  (skip2): Conv2d(16, 32, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(2, 2))
  (skip3): Conv2d(32, 64, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(2, 2))
  (classifier): Sequential(
    (0): AdaptiveAvgPool2d(output_size=(2, 2))
    (1): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
    (2): Linear(in_features=512, out_features=120, bias=True)
    (3): ReLU()
    (4): Linear(in_features=120, out_features=60, bias=True)
    (5): ReLU()
    (6): Linear(in_features=60, out_features=1, bias=True)
  )
)
